fields.title: Advanced Smartphone Chip Level Training
fields.description: Our Advanced Smartphone Chip Level Training program is designed to provide students with comprehensive knowledge and practical skills in repairing smartphones at the chip level. Through a blend of theoretical learning and hands-on experience, students will gain expertise in diagnosing and fixing hardware issues in the latest generation smartphones.

fields.title: overview
fields.description:
Our Advanced Smartphone Chip Level Training program spans 8 months, with 2 months dedicated to intensive training and 12 months for on-the-job experience with stipend. Students will master the latest smartphone repair techniques, learning from skilled faculty with 17+ years of experience. State-of-the-art labs ensure hands-on learning, preparing graduates for successful careers in mobile technology.
Training Structure:

 

The course spans over 8 months, with 2 months dedicated to intensive theoretical and practical training.

Following the training period, students undergo 12 months of on-the-job training with a stipend, gaining valuable hands-on experience in real-world scenarios.

fields.title: New Course Offering...
fields.description:
Advanced Smartphone Chip Level Training
We're excited to introduce our latest addition to the curriculum - the Advanced Smartphone Chip Level Training course. This course is meticulously crafted to provide students with in-depth knowledge and hands-on experience in repairing smartphone hardware at the chip level. Covering the most advanced techniques and troubleshooting methods, this course equips students with the expertise needed to tackle even the most complex repair tasks. Enroll now to stay ahead of the curve and unlock new opportunities in the rapidly evolving field of mobile technology.

fields.title: Industry Partnership Announcement
fields.description: We are thrilled to announce our recent collaboration with some of the industry's leading mobile technology companies. Through this partnership, IAMT students will gain access to exclusive internship opportunities, workshops conducted by industry experts, and direct pathways to job placements in renowned companies. This strategic alliance underscores our commitment to providing our students with real-world exposure and ensuring their seamless transition into the professional arena. Keep an eye on our updates as we unveil the exciting opportunities that lie ahead!

fields.title: IAMT Alumni Spotlight: Success Stories
fields.description: Join us in celebrating the achievements of our esteemed alumni who have carved out successful careers in the mobile technology industry. From launching their own smartphone repair businesses to securing coveted managerial positions in prominent companies, our graduates continue to make significant contributions to the field. Through our Alumni Spotlight series, we'll be sharing inspiring stories that showcase the diverse career paths and accomplishments of our alumni. Get ready to be motivated and inspired by the remarkable journeys of those who began their careers with IAMT.
